{"hash":"ec5e50c96b423917fd23f8317f4a3bf99d08681d","data":{"post":{"title":"Istanbul","author":"","date":"2022-10-10","content":"<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221010_122157.jpg\"></p>\n<p>En we zijn in Istanbul. Zoooo vliegveld is groot!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221010_170110.jpg\"></p>\n<p>En.. heel erg druk.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221010_172241.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_125426.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221010_170708.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Wandeling maken op de Galata brug.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_110129.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_165516.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_171907.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Even een wat rustigere plek zoeken.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_122103.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_133948.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Diep ergens in de donkere straten van Istanbul. Heerlijke kebab zaak.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_181708.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_181738.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_091336.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_184322.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Moskee bezoeken, ook binnen!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_185747.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_100150.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Galata toren.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_101555.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Uitzicht vanuit de bovenste verdieping.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_150658.jpg\"></p>\n<p>We pakken de boot om het westen en oosten van de stad te zien.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_153642.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_155202.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_160204.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_160717.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221012_161129.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221013_102253.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Topkapi Paleis</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221013_113255.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221013_113910.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Nog een uitzicht van de skyline.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221014_115042.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Een bezoek aan de Mall mag niet ontbreken.</p>\n","id":"a62793c520acf35e2cfc127c29f10371","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/istanbul/","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221011_110129.jpg","category":{"title":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","id":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Goreme","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/goreme/","id":"0d90d76e9aeea8e459ab084f0929dc87","excerpt":"Goreme ook wel bekend voor de 'Insta' luchtbalonnen en mooie landschappen."}},{"node":{"title":"Antalya","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/antalya/","id":"2ece3ea708db0595e414f89dc2859cef","excerpt":"Lekker toerist spelen en genieten van het lekkere weer."}},{"node":{"title":"Istanbul","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/istanbul/","id":"a62793c520acf35e2cfc127c29f10371","excerpt":"Istanbul. Druk."}}]}}}},"context":{}}